{"tid":822208,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《小偷家族》樹木希林離世 享年75歲","createTime":"2018-09-16T08:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T10:23:57.000Z","uid":15276,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4a46a0566d9080a6807735b3a1653e0ddc467d","tid":822208,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:25:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/16/162447_df952e601d6ad5b2d3b34e62e90644a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F16%2F162447_df952e601d6ad5b2d3b34e62e90644a7.png&h=1cb60880&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本名導是枝裕和攞獎片《小偷家族》的甘草女星樹木希林，今日被證實於昨日凌晨2時許與世長辭，享年75歲。<br />\n<br />\n樹木希林是日本老牌女星，上月13日她在樓梯跌下，導致大腿骨折，要接受緊急手術，女婿本木雅弘日前現身東京「全國統一防災模試」活動時，曾指樹木希林支氣管弱，肺亦因其癌症影響好弱，情況一度嚴重，之後好轉接受物理治療，可惜前日她在家人陪同下逝世。<br />\n<br />\n樹木希林在日本影壇甚具影響力，稱呼屬是枝裕和的愛將之一，曾參演多部影視作品，包括《東京鐵塔》、《橫山家之味》等，由於近年其身體變得虛弱，故她多次受訪也自言「嗰頭近」，並影定遺照，自言《小偷家族》可能是最後一部參演的是枝裕和電影。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180916/58688727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58688727&d=oKxhwpfRMxZjXWLFL2Yh9vM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=192412f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F58688727&h=26861298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180916/58688727</a>"},{"pid":"96a7fcc522167b042258d504e3940f1dd6e70143","tid":822208,"uid":97306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T08:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85bcf1f8143d2a0e32906d0b60f0f084f8ec7dc","tid":822208,"uid":9116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09